{"tid":1851261,"cid":33,"subCid":0,"title":"根本政府依家就係只優待警甴","createTime":"2020-01-30T03:19:25.000Z","updateTime":"2020-01-30T04:04:19.000Z","uid":120361,"like":6,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":5,"replies":[{"pid":"3b2eea1e24fd759eda28a6f147f7754f401b72ec","tid":1851261,"uid":120361,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-30T03:19:25.000Z","msg":"(突發) 消防救護缺口罩 被迫重用 口罩嚴重不足<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1851191\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1851191</a><br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區<br />\n<br />\n明眼人都知，點解各位公務員仲未起義&hellip;<br />\n咩好嘢都比曬佢，佢哋依家口罩仲多過消防、醫護，每次出更一定有得戴。<br />\n<br />\n你哋記住，係政府教我和平示威無用嘅。<br />\n<br />\n每一次唔用激進行動佢都唔理<img src=\"/assets/faces/lny/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n唉，我講咁多係無用，我唔係公務員，但我知道公務員(包括醫護)反抗嘅威力係勁過我哋，佢哋點攬警甴都好，佢叫唔到警甴做你哋嘅野，反而你哋可以代替佢。"},{"pid":"2d4078b49ec4025f4163d319d77557ce20003a2e","tid":1851261,"uid":14918,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-30T03:22:35.000Z","msg":"公務員 = 777&rsquo;s pets"},{"pid":"1806005a28ccf5d37298c5d157c02261dfef5fb0","tid":1851261,"uid":91897,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-01-30T03:25:16.000Z","msg":"有眼睇, 警甴全部都係帶深綠色CSI 款口罩咁濟<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"948a76cf91c7cbe599e477e9e3addf9104b8274a","tid":1851261,"uid":120361,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"1806005a28ccf5d37298c5d157c02261dfef5fb0","tid":1851261,"uid":91897,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-01-30T03:25:16.000Z","msg":"有眼睇, 警甴全部都係帶深綠色CSI 款口罩咁濟<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-30T03:26:26.000Z","msg":"根本就比曬佢哋"},{"pid":"4e01eb59fb50201ba3b124c81903e79b076721d4","tid":1851261,"uid":173844,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-30T03:59:48.000Z","msg":"罷工啦 保住自己先救到更多人<br /